Air Freight

TIS LOGISTIC provides international, domestic and charter air transportation services. We deliver cargo by air worldwide in the shortest possible time.

Air freight types

We will deliver your cargo from anywhere in the world*. A wide agent network, representative offices in different countries and direct agreements with major air carriers allow us to offer our customers the best possible airfares

*Limitations apply, please contact the company manager directly for more detailed advice.

Air transportation within Russia

Our domestic network covers Moscow, St. Petersburg, Novosibirsk, Khabarovsk, Vladivostok and other major cities. We organize air cargo transportation of any objects: hazardous, sensitive, perishable, oversized - and you can manage the process as if you were the commander of the aircraft

Air charter transportation

We organize individual air charter services for project cargoes. If necessary, we rent a whole airplane, if the volume allows us to fill the entire cargo compartment
